sources.description:
*Blood Lake: Attack of the Killer Lampreys* - After chomping through the fish population, thousands of starved lampreys begin attacking the citizens of a sleepy lake town, and the community scrambles to stay alive.
2014.  Stars: Shannen Doherty, Jason Brooks, Zack Ward, Christopher Lloyd

*Clown* - A group of teens fights for their lives as they find themselves trapped in a fun-house, stalked by a killer clown who won't rest until every last one of them is dead.
2019. Stars: Adam Elshar, Dave Klec, Micavrie Amaia
